OL,3,CElderly couple jailed after racial
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FAn elderly couple who were filmed
OL,7,Fracially abusing a Filipino nurse in a
OL,8,Fpark have been jailed.
OL,10,FA video of Michael Bairstow, 77, and
OL,11,Fhis 72-year-old wife Fyona making
OL,12,Fracist comments and assaulting Apple
OL,13,FMoorhouse went viral following the
OL,14,Fincident in Manor Heath Park, Halifax,
OL,15,Flast August.
OL,17,FThe couple, who had already admitted
OL,18,Fracially aggravated assault at
OL,19,FBradford Magistrates Court, were both
OL,20,Fjailed for eight weeks.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
