PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776359146
OL,3,CElderly couple jailed after racial
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FBefore begin deliberations over their
OL,7,Fsentence, chairwoman of the bench Gill
OL,8,FArnold told the couple to stand,
OL,9,Fsaying: "That somebody can be so vile
OL,10,Fand aggressive to somebody such as
OL,11,Fthis young woman here ` I can only
OL,12,Fthink you must be extremely ashamed."
OL,14,FShe added: "I'm glad you are hanging
OL,15,Fyour head, and we'll be extremely fair
OL,16,Fwhen we decide what's going to happen
OL,17,Fto you, but I want you to know, as
OL,18,Fanother human being, I feel sickened.
OL,20,F"It's just dreadful and you should be
OL,21,Fdeeply ashamed."
OL,26,@qD@IOUtD@eO]vD@LOU|D@AOU}D@PO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
