OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776359146
OL,3,CElderly couple jailed after racial
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FMichael Bairstow replied: "We are
OL,7,Fashamed."
OL,9,FThe court heard the couple, who
OL,10,Farrived at court with their faces
OL,11,Fcovered, became aggressive with Ms
OL,12,FMoorhouse when their dog started
OL,13,Fbarking at her children, and she told
OL,14,Fthem it should be on a lead.
OL,16,FDuring the "prolonged" confrontation
OL,17,FMichael Bairstow told her to "go back
OL,18,Fto your dinghy" while making rowing
OL,19,Fgestures at her, and Fyona Bairstow
OL,20,Fpulled her ponytail when she tried to
OL,21,Fwalk away.
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@IO]xD@LOUxD@VO]yD@^OUzD@OO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
