PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776359146
OL,3,CElderly couple jailed after racial
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FMs Moorhouse sobbed in court as mobile
OL,7,Fphone footage of the incident was
OL,8,Fplayed in court showing Michael
OL,9,FBairstow telling his dog to "get her,
OL,10,Fkill" before picking up a dog bowl
OL,11,Ffull of water and throwing it at her.
OL,13,FFyona Bairstow could then be seen
OL,14,Fmaking a reference to slavery and
OL,15,Fmocking Ms Moorhouse's father, saying:
OL,16,F"You can't even speak English."
OL,18,FMichael Bairstow asked Ms Moorhouse if
OL,19,Fshe had "come from a rubber boat" and
OL,20,Frepeatedly said: "Ban the immigrants."
OL,26,@qD@]OUrD@EO]xD@AOUxD@_O]{D@IOU{D@aO]|D@
OL,26,AROU|D@fO]
