PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776359146
OL,3,CElderly couple jailed after racial
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FThe court heard that Ms Moorhouse told
OL,7,Fthe couple she was a healthcare worker
OL,8,Fand entitled to remain in the UK.
OL,10,FAs she tried to walk away, Fyona
OL,11,FBairstow pulled her backwards by her
OL,12,Fponytail.
OL,14,FThe court heard that when another
OL,15,Fwoman intervened and told Michael
OL,16,FBairstow to get away from Ms
OL,17,FMoorhouse, he punched her to the left
OL,18,Fside of her face and said: "Sticking
OL,19,Fup for immigrants, who do you think
OL,20,Fyou are?"
OL,26,@zD@\OU|D@IO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
