OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776359146
OL,3,CElderly couple jailed after racial
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FIn mitigation, Raza Hussain,
OL,7,Frepresenting the Bairstows, said the
OL,8,Fincident was not pre-meditated and the
OL,9,Fcouple "fully accept the racial
OL,10,Flanguage they used was wholly
OL,11,Finappropriate, which they deeply
OL,12,Fregret".
OL,14,FMr Hussain went on to say: "The fact
OL,15,Fthat this incident was circulated
OL,16,Fwidely on social media and on national
OL,17,Fnews has brought them significant
OL,18,Fembarrassment."
OL,26,@qD@HOUtD@GO]vD@\OUzD@OO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
