OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776359146
OL,3,CElderly couple jailed after racial
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FIn a victim personal statement read in
OL,7,Fcourt, Ms Moorhouse said she was
OL,8,F"scared for my life" during the
OL,9,Fincident and now carries a panic
OL,10,Fbutton with her.
OL,12,FMs Arnold told the couple "That kind
OL,13,Fof attitude and those words and the
OL,14,Fthings you said to Ms Moorhouse, is
OL,15,Fnot something that comes out of the
OL,16,Fblue in a second, it's something
OL,17,Fdeeply rooted."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]tD@[OU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
