CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776359146
OL,3,CElderly couple jailed after racial
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FShe said the fact that children were
OL,7,Fpresent at the time meant only an
OL,8,Fimmediate custodial sentence could be
OL,9,Fjustified.
OL,11,FThe couple, of Shelf, Halifax, were
OL,12,Fboth ordered to pay #175 compensation
OL,13,Fto Ms Moorhouse. Michael Bairstow, who
OL,14,Falso admitted assaulting the woman who
OL,15,Ftried to intervene, was told to to pay
OL,16,Fher #100.
OL,18,FSpeaking after the sentencing, Ms
OL,19,FMoorhouse said: "It's a clear message
OL,20,Fthat we're all equal, that racism is
OL,21,Fnot acceptable.
OL,26,@{D@QOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
